{"title_page": "Naval Calling Station Luderitz", "text_new": "{{Infobox military installation\n|name= Naval Calling Station Luderitz\n|ensign= \n|native_name= \n|partof= <!-- for elements within a larger site -->\n|location= \n|nearest_town= [[Luderitz]]<!-- used in military test site infobox -->\n|country= {{NAM}}\n|image= \n|caption= \n|pushpin_map= \n|pushpin_label_position= \n|pushpin_mapsize= \n|pushpin_map_caption= \n|coordinates= \n|type= [[Naval Station]]\n|site_area= <!-- area of site m2, km2 square mile etc -->\n|height= <!-- height of tallest part, not above sea level -->\n|ownership= [[Ministry of Defence (Namibia)]]<!--government department such as the MoD or the United States DoD-->\n|operator= [[Namibian Navy]] <!--where different from ownership such as the RAF or the USAF-->\n|controlledby= [[Namibian Defence Force]] <!--such as RAF Bomber Command or the Eighth Air Force-->\n|open_to_public= <!--for out of use sites/sites with museums etc-->\n|condition= Active\n|built= <!-- {{Start date|YYYY}} -->\n|builder= \n|used= <!--{{End date|1946}} -->\n|materials= \n|fate= <!--changed from demolished parameter-->\n|battles= \n|events= \n|current_commander= Commander Natangwe Hekandjo\n|past_commanders= <!-- past notable commander(s) -->\n|garrison= <!-- such as the 25th Bombardment Group -->\n|occupants= <!-- squadrons only -->\n|TC= \n|LID= \n|GPS= \n|WMO= \n|website= \n|footnotes= \n}}\n'''Naval Calling Station Luderitz''' is a naval station of the [[Namibian Navy]]. It is located in [[ILuderitz]] on Namibia South Atlantic coast.\n\n==Current Status==\nThe station is currently active.\n\n==Commandants==\n{{Post-start|caption=Naval Base Impalilaa|float=}}\n{{Post-header|post-name=Commandant}}\n{{Post-member|from-date=21 June 2019|post-incumbent=Commander Natangwe Hekandjo<ref>https://neweralive.na/posts/change-of-command-at-naval-calling-station</ref>\n||to-date=Incumbent}}\n<!--{{Post-member|from-date=XXX|post-incumbent=XXX|to-date=XXX}} -->\n{{Post-end}}\